/*!
 * \page SiteManagement Site management selenium tests
 *
 * \section SecNewSit New site
 *  Test for adding a new site to the application.
 *  It creates a new 'test' site. This are the parameters given to the new site:
 *    - Site 	   		  : 'Site test'
 *    - Order			  : '1'
 *    - Module			  : 'AweMod2'
 *    - DataBase		  : 'AWEMADSQS01 (Production-Datasource)'
 *    - Active     		  : 'Yes' (1)
 *
 * \section SecSitViw View site
 *  Test for verifying that the added site is correct.
 *  This process search the name of the new site in the correspondent criterion
 *  of site management window, it selects it and goes to 'View' window to visualise it.
 *
 * \section SecChangeSit Update site
 *  Test for modifying a defined site.
 *  This process search the name of the new site in the correspondent criterion
 *  of site management window, it selects it and goes to 'Update' window to modify it.
 *  Afterwards, it changes the profile to which it is assigned setting name to 'Site changed' 
 *  and database name to 'DBORAMiercoles (Preproduction-Datasource)' and confirmes the modifications.
 *
 * \section SecViwChangeSit View updated site
 *  Test for verifying that the modifications made on the site are correct.
 *  This process search the name of the updated site in the correspondent criterion
 *  of site management window, it selects it and goes to 'View' window to to visualise it.
 *
 * \section SecSitDel Delete site
 *  Test for verifying the delete of one site.
 *  This process search the name of the 'Site changed' site in the correspondent criterion
 *  of site management window, it selects it and pushes 'Delete' button to delete it.
 *
 * \section SecViwDelSit Verify Delete site
 *  Test for verifying that the delete of site 'Site changed' was correct.
 */
